1.addscoreDesc: 每次使用热水袋可获得10积分
dogTalk: I like your facial expression when you failed to catch me!
Ughhh... Master, take me home, I am hungry!
Come and get me! When you get me, I'll let you... hehehe!

I want to fly even higher, so that I can pee further!
1.maxRewardDesc: Limited Merlin for Treasure Hunt event! Break the Limit and Let Holy Light Protect You!
